<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">看到这只与爱犬外貌如此相似的狗狗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上一双拉布拉多标志性耳朵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铲屎官也从来没有怀疑过它的“身份”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201009/8f63dac382504ff581044290c1d2ffca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果两个月后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铲屎官开始觉得有些不对劲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为这只“拉拉”的耳朵居然立起来了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（正常来说，拉布拉多是不会立耳的）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201009/7200a1277cfc4158ad546c5f166df993.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">震惊之余</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铲屎官赶紧带着狗子去了趟宠物医院</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后她被医生告知</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是一只血统纯正的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中华田园犬…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201009/ec6c4c225df240fdaaae1326bd9cd9d3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想养一只拉布拉多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却意外养到了一只中华田园犬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">关键它们小时候还那么相似…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不得不说这也是一段神奇的缘分呢</p>